---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about John VonDrashek, a Ruthenian Catholic software developer passionate about faith and technology.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
  </section>

  <div class="about-content">
    <section class="section intro-section">
      <div class="intro-image">
        <img src="/images/met-virgin-eleousa.jpg" alt="Byzantine icon of the Virgin Eleousa from the Metropolitan Museum of Art" />
      </div>
      <div class="intro-text">
        <h2 class="section-title">Who I Am</h2>
        <p>
          I'm a Ruthenian Catholic software developer with a passion for creating tools that serve both
          practical needs and higher purposes. My faith isn't separate from my work—it's
          woven into everything I do, from the projects I choose to build to the care I put
          into crafting quality software.
        </p>
        <p>
          As part of the Byzantine Catholic tradition, I draw inspiration from the rich iconographic
          and liturgical heritage of the Eastern Church while remaining in full communion with Rome.
        </p>
        <p>
          When I'm not coding, you can find me exploring Church history, playing games,
          or finding new ways to integrate faith and technology.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">What I Do</h2>
      <div class="skills-grid">
        <div class="skill-card">
          <h3>Faith-Integrated Software</h3>
          <p>
            I build applications that help people grow in their spiritual lives, from
            prayer timers to educational tools exploring Catholic history.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-card">
          <h3>Game Development Tools</h3>
          <p>
            I create libraries and tools for game developers, specializing in MonoGame,
            procedural generation, and .NET game development.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-card">
          <h3>Developer Experience</h3>
          <p>
            I build VSCode extensions and source generators that make developers' lives
            easier—because good tooling matters.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Technologies</h2>
      <div class="tech-list">
        <div class="tech-category">
          <h3>Languages</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>C# / .NET</li>
            <li>TypeScript</li>
            <li>React</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-category">
          <h3>Game Dev</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>MonoGame</li>
            <li>Procedural Generation</li>
            <li>Myra UI</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-category">
          <h3>Tools</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Roslyn (Source Generators)</li>
            <li>VSCode Extensions</li>
            <li>Git / GitHub</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section cta-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Let's Connect</h2>
      <p>
        Interested in collaborating on a project, have a question about my work, or just
        want to say hello? I'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .intro-section {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .intro-image {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 250px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    border: 3px solid var(--color-gold);
  }

  .intro-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .intro-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .intro-section {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .intro-image {
      width: 200px;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    }
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .skill-card {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .skill-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .skill-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .tech-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .tech-category h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .tech-category ul {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .tech-category li {
    padding: 0.25em 0;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-md);
  }
</style>
